Package: ggcomplex
Title: Complex Composite Plots Based on ggplot2 Grammar of Graphics
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Developer", "Name", email = "dev@example.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: A toolkit for drawing complex composite plots (heatmaps with
    dendrograms, side annotations, and more) using the ggplot2 layer grammar.
    It integrates ggtree for tree rendering and aplot for subplot alignment,
    providing a pipeline-style API that is both intuitive and extensible.
